OL,3,CReview finds PSNI unlawfully spied on
OL,4,Cjournalists
OL,6,FA review into the use of police
OL,7,Fsurveillance has revealed the PSNI
OL,8,Fmade 21 unlawful attempts to uncover
OL,9,Fthe sources of eight journalists in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland by spying on them
OL,11,Fthrough their phones.
OL,13,FHowever, Angus McCullough KC's review
OL,14,Ffound the surveillance of journalists
OL,15,Fand lawyers by police was not
OL,16,F"widespread or systemic".
