OL,6,FMr McCullough KC described the
OL,7,Fpractice as "disturbing" saying
OL,8,Fconfidence in policing in Northern
OL,9,FIreland had been lost. He said the
OL,10,Frecommendations would ensure the
OL,11,Ffuture of the organisation.
OL,13,FChief Constable Jon Boutcher accepted
OL,14,Fthe review and its recommendations. He
OL,15,Fsaid there were no grounds for a
OL,16,Fpublic inquiry. He said the report had
OL,17,Ffound deficiencies
