OL,3,CReview finds PSNI unlawfully spied on
OL,4,Cjournalists
OL,6,FThe PSNI Chief Constable was forced to
OL,7,Fset up the independent review last
OL,8,FJune after a court ruled police had
OL,9,Funlawfully spied on Belfast
OL,10,Fjournalists, Barry McCaffrey and
OL,11,FTrevor Birney in an attempt to uncover
OL,12,Ftheir sources.
OL,14,FThe team made up of experts in law and
OL,15,Fhuman rights has been investigating
OL,16,Fthe use of surveillance between
OL,17,FJanuary 2011 and November 2024.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
