OL,3,CReview finds PSNI unlawfully spied on
OL,4,Cjournalists
OL,6,FThe review had particular concern over
OL,7,Fwhat was described as the 'washing
OL,8,Fthrough' of a lengthy list of
OL,9,Fjournalists telephone numbers in a so-
OL,10,Fcalled 'defensive operation' to
OL,11,Fidentify unauthorised contact between
OL,12,FPSNI officers or employees and
OL,13,Fjournalists.
OL,15,FThis was not compatible with human
OL,16,Frights, the review found.
