OL,6,FThe practice was formally discontinued
OL,7,Fin May 2024 and had been ongoing for a
OL,8,Fnumber of years. The report proposes
OL,9,Fthis be considered for self referral
OL,10,Fby the PSNI to the Information
OL,11,FCommissioner.
OL,13,FThe McCullough Review has made 16
OL,14,Frecommendations and it is understood
OL,15,FChief Constable Jon Butcher has made
OL,16,Fapologies to some journalists involved.
