OL,6,FHuman rights organisations Amnesty
OL,7,FInternational and the Committee on
OL,8,FAdministration of Justice have written
OL,9,Fto the Secretary of State for Northern
OL,10,FIreland to ask him to establish a
OL,11,Fpublic inquiry into covert
OL,12,Fsurveillance in Northern Ireland by
OL,13,FMI5, and the establishment of the
OL,14,FCovert Commissioner for Law
OL,15,FEnforcement for Northern Ireland
OL,16,Ffollowing publication of a report
OL,17,Fdetailing a catalogue of wrongdoing by
OL,18,Fthe PSNI.
