OL,3,CReview finds PSNI unlawfully spied on
OL,4,Cjournalists
OL,6,FPatrick Corrigan, Northern Ireland
OL,7,FDirector of Amnesty International UK,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This report exposes a
OL,9,Fdisturbing pattern of unlawful covert
OL,10,Fsurveillance of journalists, with the
OL,11,FPSNI showing clear disregard for press
OL,12,Ffreedom and the rule of law.
OL,14,F"The scale of the wrongdoing is
OL,15,Falarming, from repeated attempts to
OL,16,Fidentify reporters' sources to covert
OL,17,Foperations concealed from oversight
OL,18,Fbodies.
