OL,4,Cjournalists
OL,6,F"But questions remain. How far has MI5
OL,7,Fgone in unlawfully monitoring
OL,8,Fjournalists in Northern Ireland? A
OL,9,Ffree press simply cannot function
OL,10,Funder the shadow of state
OL,11,Fsurveillance. That is why we are
OL,12,Fasking the Secretary of State to set
OL,13,Fup a full public inquiry. Only full
OL,14,Fdisclosure can restore trust and
OL,15,Fsafeguard the rights of journalists in
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland."
